en.codex: Become the bastion that defends allies using powerful healing abilities with Trinity Prime. Featuring altered mod polarities for greater customization.
en.description:
Release Date: October 6th, 2015

Trinity Prime is the primed variant of the Trinity Warframe featuring more powerful stats: possessing a higher shield capacity and sprint speed, as well as having an additional and polarity.

ru.description: Станьте бастионом, защищающим союзников с помощью мощных исцеляющих умений в качестве Тринити прайм. Содержит измененные слоты поляризации для лучшей конфигурации
